Low-Light Vision																	KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Low-Light Vision		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:A whisper gnome can see twice as far as a human in starlight, moonlight, and similar conditions of poor illumination. He retains the ability to distinguish color and detail under these conditions.																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.96
Darkvision																		KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Darkvision			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:Whisper gnomes can see in the dark out to 60 feet. Darkvision is black and white only, but it is otherwise like normal sight, and whisper gnomes can function just fine with no light at all.																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.96
+1 racial bonus on attack rolls against kobolds and goblinoids (including goblins, hobgoblins, and bugbears)	KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Racial Attack Bonus		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:Like their more common cousins, whisper gnomes battle these creatures frequently and practice special techniques for fighting them.																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.96
+4 dodge bonus to Armor Class against monsters of the giant type (such as ogres, trolls, and hill giants)		KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Racial AC Bonus			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:This bonus represents special training that whisper gnomes undergo, during which they learn tricks that previous generations developed in their battles with giants. Any time a creature loses its Dexterity bonus (if any) to Armor Class, such as when it's caught flatfooted, it loses its dodge bonus, too. The Monster Manual has information on which creatures are of the giant type.									SOURCEPAGE:p.96
+4 racial bonus on Hide and Move Silently checks											KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Racial Stealth Bonus		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:Whisper gnomes have an uncanny knack for stealth.																																																								BONUS:SKILL|Hide,Move Silently|4|TYPE=Racial	SOURCEPAGE:p.96
+2 racial bonus on Listen and Spot checks													KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Racial Perception Bonus	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:Whisper gnomes have keen eyes and ears.																																																										BONUS:SKILL|Listen,Spot|2|TYPE=Racial		SOURCEPAGE:p.96
Weapon Familiarity																KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Weapon Familiarity		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:Whisper gnomes may treat gnome hooked hammers as martial weapons rather than exotic weapons.																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.96
Spell-Like Abilities																KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Spell-Like Abilities		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality	SPELLS:Racial|TIMES=1|TIMEUNIT=Day|CASTERLEVEL=1|Ghost Sound|Mage Hand|Message|Silence (Self Only)	DESC:Spell-Like Abilities - 1/day - ghost sound, mage hand, message, silence (silence can only be cast on the Whisper Gnome himself). Caster level 1st; save DC 10 + whisper gnome's Cha modifier + spell level.																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.96
Racial Feats																	KEY:Whisper Gnome ~ Racial Feats			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.WhisperGnome Race Trait.SpecialQuality																		DESC:The Extra Silence and Silencing Strike feats can be taken by whisper gnome characters (see Chapter 6: Character Options).																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.96


